Melanie Robbins is an American television host, global motivational speaker and best-selling author of The 5 Second Rule, Stop Saying You’re Fine, Take Control of Your Life, Kick Ass with Mel Robbins and The 5 Second Journal. Mel helps people transform their lives by empowering them with the tools necessary to conquer their everyday problems and life’s biggest problems. Ambition If you think of the word “Ambition”, what person comes to mind: the CEO of a start-up company, an entrepreneur that makes millions, a celebrity, a pro-athlete that lives in a mansion or a visionary that is trying to change the world. If these doesn’t inspire you – this is the video for you!  <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-18659" src="https://thenewspaper.b-cdn.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Mel-Robbins.jpeg" alt="" width="800" height="533" srcset="https://thenewspaper.b-cdn.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Mel-Robbins.jpeg 800w, https://thenewspaper.b-cdn.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Mel-Robbins-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://thenewspaper.b-cdn.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Mel-Robbins-696x464.jpeg 696w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" />  Now that you have seen ambition in yourself, help someone else to see it in themselves by sharing the video with them. For more information